additives_n.description: Number of food additives present in the product

additives_tags.description: List of food additives identifiers used in the product

allergens_tags.description: List of allergens present in the product, identified by standardized tags

brands_tags.description: List of brand tags, used to classify products by their brand names.
known_issues: Some brands may have multiple tags.

examples: usda organic Butternut Mountain Farm,Butternut Mountain Farm

categories_tags.description: List of food categories in the form of tags, allowing products to be classified according to different criteria.

code.description: Product barcode (EAN-13 or internal codes for food stores). Products without barcodes are assigned numbers starting with prefix 200

countries_tags.description: List of countries where the product is sold, identified by standardized country codes

created_t.description: Date when the product was first added to the database (UNIX timestamp)

creator.description: Username of the contributor who first added the product to the database

ecoscore_grade.description: Environmental impact grade from A to E, where A represents the lowest environmental impact

labels.description: Food quality labels and certifications associated with the product
examples: Fair trade, No gluten, Organic, Vegetarian, Kosher, No GMOs, Vegan, Canada Organic, Fairtrade USA...

lang.description: Primary language used for product information

last_modified_t.description: date that the product page was last modified

last_updated_t.description: Unix timestamp of the last modification to the product data

manufacturing_places.description: Locations where the product is manufactured or processed

minerals_tags.description: List of minerals present in the product

nova_group.description: NOVA classification group (1-4) indicating the degree of food processing. 1 = Unprocessed or minimally processed foods, 2 = Processed culinary ingredients, 3 = Processed foods, 4 = Ultra-processed foods.

nutriments.description: Detailed nutritional information including nutrients, values per 100g and per serving
nutriments.type: STRUCT("name" VARCHAR, "value" FLOAT, "100g" FLOAT, serving FLOAT, unit VARCHAR, prepared_value FLOAT, prepared_100g FLOAT, prepared_serving FLOAT, prepared_unit VARCHAR)[]

nutriscore_grade.description: Product's Nutri-Score grade from A to E, where A represents the best nutritional quality

packaging.description: Physical packaging characteristics including shape, material, and container type

packagings.type: STRUCT(material VARCHAR, number_of_units BIGINT, quantity_per_unit VARCHAR, quantity_per_unit_unit VARCHAR, quantity_per_unit_value VARCHAR, recycling VARCHAR, shape VARCHAR, weight_measured FLOAT)[]
